before mee yo of 20th past the patternes do not please I would

to demand there by the dead of the datchess of bavaria,
will ronder all our nobilitie i'eittie officiers in morsinge so
I doubt no demand for mode cullours the next lent att least
I can in order non yett inclosed some instructions for northrens
